				"a(n) = (n! (n-1) Gamma(n-1/2) / Gamma(1/2) ) * 1F1[2-n; 3/2-n; -1/2] [Erlebach and Ruehr]. This representation is exact, asymptotic and convergent.",
				"2*a(n) -2*n*(n-1)*a(n-1) -n*(n-1)^2*a(n-2)=0.",
